[1] Sierra Leone: 9th doctor infected with Ebola
Date: 26 Nov 2014
Source: AP [edited]
http://hosted2.ap.org/APDEFAULT/bbd825583c8542898e6fa7d440b9febc/Article_2014-11-26-AF--Ebola-West%20Africa/id-e99d37fe90d84a82b98576660f6dc6ce


An official says a 9th Sierra Leonean doctor has been infected with Ebola, underscoring the devastating toll the disease is taking on health care workers. Abass Kamara, a Health Ministry spokesman, said that a top military doctor tested positive for Ebola on Wed [26 Nov 2014]. He was working at the Hastings Ebola treatment center in the east end of the capital [Monrovia]... more

